From: "Lorenzo Stoakes (Oracle)" <ljs@kernel.org>
Date: Wed, 18 Mar 2026 15:50:29 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] mm: update vma_supports_mlock() to use new VMA flags

We now have the ability to test all of this using the new vma_flags_t
approach, so let's do so.

Link: https://lkml.kernel.org/r/8bd076169508ea4640f66f91c4b84b433a3476f1.1773846935.git.ljs@kernel.org
Signed-off-by: Lorenzo Stoakes (Oracle) <ljs@kernel.org>
Cc: Albert Ou <aou@eecs.berkeley.edu>
Cc: Alexander Gordeev <agordeev@linux.ibm.com>
